.demo
  %h3
    =image_tag("icons/22x22/grid.png", :border => 0)
    =@title
  %center
    %table#invheaders_demo0503.scroll{ :cellspacing => "0", :cellpadding => "0" }
    #invheaders_demo0503_pager.scroll{ :style => "text-align:center;" }

/ End demo 
.demo-description
  %p    
    This example shows online editing and saving a row. This is done when the user clicks on a row.
  %p
    Note the use of a second parameter of 
    %code
      editRow
    method. This way when we press Enter data is saved
    to the server and when we press ESC key the editing is canceled.
/ End demo-description
